      <title>美国银行认为期限风险抑制公司债券需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bofa-sees-duration-risk-curbing-demand-for-corporate-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师预计，今年降息次数减少的前景将削弱对较长期投资级债券的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bofa-sees-duration-risk-curbing-demand-for-corporate-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
