    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省省长警告称，特朗普的关税即将到来，将包括石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯在佛罗里达会见美国当选总统后警告称，一旦唐纳德·特朗普下周就任总统，加拿大人应该准备好面对美国关税，石油产品将不会受到豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙拟对非欧盟公民购房征收 100% 税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/spain-to-try-to-limit-real-estate-purchases-by-non-eu-residents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙要求非欧盟居民在该国购房时缴纳高达 100% 的税，此举可能会影响来自英国和拉丁美洲的买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/spain-to-try-to-limit-real-estate-purchases-by-non-eu-residents</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国对俄罗斯的制裁威胁供应，油价创下五个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，威胁到全球最大产油国之一的石油供应，油价上涨至五个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
